<div id="m-msg-fake-poly-0002" data-section-uuid="msg-fake-poly-0002" class="msg msg--openai">

## 2370-10-25 08:03:20 UTC — gpt-5

```python
import numpy as np
x = np.array([1,2,3,4,5])
y = np.array([2.1, 4.0, 9.1, 15.8, 25.0])
coeffs = np.polyfit(x, y, 2)
print(coeffs)
```

